        <p>teḷ <lb break="no" n="2"></lb>ḷāṟṟ’ eṟintu <lb n="3"></lb><hi rend="grantha">rājya</hi><unclear>mu</unclear>ṅ ko <lb break="no" n="4"></lb>ṇṭa nanti-p <lb break="no" n="5"></lb>-pōttaraiyar<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied> <lb break="no" n="6"></lb>ku yāṇṭu Iru <lb break="no" n="7"></lb>patt-oṉṟ-āvatu</p>
        <p><lb n="8"></lb>parāntakapurat <lb break="no" n="9"></lb>tu Aṟinti <lb break="no" n="10"></lb>kai-<hi rend="grantha">Īśvaragṛ</hi> <lb break="no" n="11"></lb><hi rend="grantha">haṃ śāsa</hi>na <lb break="no" n="12"></lb>t=tāl uṭaiyo <lb break="no" n="13"></lb>rum <gap quantity="4" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> <lb n="14"></lb><gap quantity="4" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> taḷi <lb break="no" n="15"></lb>yilāt’ āki niṉṟa <hi rend="grantha">bhaṭṭar</hi>-ēṉ māvali-y-ani <lb break="no" n="16"></lb>ya<hi rend="grantha">sthā</hi>nam-āḷvāṉ cē<unclear>vaṇaṟ kuṇṭu</unclear> ko <lb break="no" n="17"></lb>ṇṭu vantu maṭamuñ cuṭṭu-k kātta ś<choice>
            <sic>
              <hi rend="grantha">i</hi>
            </sic>
            <corr>
              <hi rend="grantha">rī</hi>
            </corr>
          </choice>-<hi rend="grantha">gura</hi> <lb break="no" n="18"></lb>varaiyum eṟintu Ivar <hi rend="grantha">śiṣya</hi>n Oru <hi rend="grantha">brā</hi> <lb break="no" n="19"></lb><hi rend="grantha">hma</hi>ṇaṉ cattimuṟṟa-t-tēvan ṟuṇṭu pa <lb break="no" n="20"></lb>ṭṭāṉ valluva-<unclear>ṉāṭ</unclear>ṭāṉ</p>
